sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant MCP as MCP / UI / REST
    participant Search as Search Module
    participant Embedder as EmbeddingModel
    participant TFIDF as TFIDFEmbedder
    participant IDFETS as IDF Table (ETS)
    participant Ollama as Ollama API
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant DB
    participant Graph as RelationshipGraph
    participant Boost as GraphBoost
    participant Telemetry as Telemetry

    User->>MCP: search_code("parse", 10)
    MCP->>Search: search_code("parse", 10)
    Search->>Telemetry: [:nexus, :search, :query] start

    Search->>Embedder: embed("parse")
    alt Ollama available
        Embedder->>Ollama: POST /api/embed (embeddinggemma:300m default; OLLAMA_MODEL env var)
        Ollama-->>Embedder: embeddings
        Embedder-->>Search: dense vector [768 dims]
    else Ollama unavailable
        Embedder-->>Search: {:error, _}
        Search->>TFIDF: embed("parse")
        TFIDF->>IDFETS: read IDF values (concurrent, no lock)
        IDFETS-->>TFIDF: IDF map
        TFIDF-->>Search: dense vector [768 dims]
    end

    Search->>TFIDF: sparse_vector("parse")
    TFIDF->>IDFETS: read IDF values
    TFIDF-->>Search: sparse vector (indices + values)

    Search->>Qdrant: hybrid_search(dense, sparse, limit=30)
    Note over Qdrant: Prefetch dense + sparse<br/>RRF fusion (server-side)<br/>30s HTTP timeout
    Qdrant-->>Search: top-30 results + payloads

    Search->>Search: deduplicate by name + type

    Search->>Graph: build_graph(results)
    Graph->>Graph: build_name_index (O(1) lookups)
    Graph->>Graph: count incoming edges (indexed)
    Graph-->>Search: graph structure

    Search->>Boost: apply_graph_boost(results, graph)
    Boost->>Boost: seed = top 5 by score
    Boost->>Boost: boost seeds (+0.1)
    Boost->>Boost: boost by incoming refs
    Boost->>Boost: boost by calls to seeds
    Boost-->>Search: re-ranked results

    Search->>Search: sort by combined score, take top-10
    Search->>Telemetry: [:nexus, :search, :query] complete
    Search-->>MCP: {:ok, results} (safe JSON encode)
    MCP-->>User: ranked code entities

    Note over Search,Graph: Graph boost brings related<br/>code closer to top results
    Note over TFIDF,IDFETS: ETS read_concurrency:<br/>no GenServer bottleneck<br/>for concurrent searches
